channel.title: Blue - F0yders (Probably my best song in a while.)
channel.description:
I had been sitting on a tune for a while and finally decided to expand on it, this is what came out of it:
https://soundcloud.com/f0ydersmusic/blue
I honestly think it is my best track in a while. Constructive criticism is always welcome.
